{"nodes":[{"pos":[12,61],"content":"Compiler Warning (level 1) C4547 | Microsoft Docs","needQuote":false,"needEscape":true,"nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Warning (level 1) C4547 | Microsoft Docs","pos":[0,49]}]},{"content":"Compiler Warning (level 1) C4547","pos":[609,641]},{"content":"'operator' : operator before comma has no effect; expected operator with side-effect","pos":[642,726]},{"content":"The compiler detected an ill-formed comma expression.","pos":[733,786]},{"content":"This warning is off by default.","pos":[793,824]},{"content":"For more information, see <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>Compiler Warnings That Are Off by Default<ept id=\"p1\">](../../preprocessor/compiler-warnings-that-are-off-by-default.md)</ept>.","pos":[825,960],"source":" For more information, see [Compiler Warnings That Are Off by Default](../../preprocessor/compiler-warnings-that-are-off-by-default.md)."},{"content":"The following sample generates C4547:","pos":[967,1004]}],"content":"---\ntitle: \"Compiler Warning (level 1) C4547 | Microsoft Docs\"\nms.custom: \"\"\nms.date: \"11/04/2016\"\nms.reviewer: \"\"\nms.suite: \"\"\nms.technology: \n  - \"devlang-cpp\"\nms.tgt_pltfrm: \"\"\nms.topic: \"error-reference\"\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"C4547\"\ndev_langs: \n  - \"C++\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"C4547\"\nms.assetid: 3edf1c2e-c0d5-444d-ae83-44a7cce24bb2\ncaps.latest.revision: 7\nauthor: \"corob-msft\"\nms.author: \"corob\"\nmanager: \"ghogen\"\ntranslation.priority.ht: \n  - \"cs-cz\"\n  - \"de-de\"\n  - \"es-es\"\n  - \"fr-fr\"\n  - \"it-it\"\n  - \"ja-jp\"\n  - \"ko-kr\"\n  - \"pl-pl\"\n  - \"pt-br\"\n  - \"ru-ru\"\n  - \"tr-tr\"\n  - \"zh-cn\"\n  - \"zh-tw\"\n---\n# Compiler Warning (level 1) C4547\n'operator' : operator before comma has no effect; expected operator with side-effect  \n  \n The compiler detected an ill-formed comma expression.  \n  \n This warning is off by default. For more information, see [Compiler Warnings That Are Off by Default](../../preprocessor/compiler-warnings-that-are-off-by-default.md).  \n  \n The following sample generates C4547:  \n  \n```  \n// C4547.cpp  \n// compile with: /W1  \n#pragma warning (default : 4547)  \nint i = 0;  \nint j = 1;  \nint main() {  \n   int l = (i != i,0);   // C4547  \n   // try the following line instead  \n   // int l = (i != i);  \n   // or  \n   // int l = ((void)(i != i),0);  \n}  \n```"}